00:32:03,170 --> 00:32:08,580
Zheng Youde retried the debtor's wife and the truth was revealed.

527
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:12,140
How did you know it?

528
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:15,489
I also know another vendetta case on the 5th day of the 7th lunar month, the year before last.

529
00:32:15,489 --> 00:32:18,260
The murderer robbed and killed, disguised as a bandit.

530
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:20,809
