The culprit was finally arrested.

535
00:32:34,150 --> 00:32:36,039
I examined this case. I know it.

536
00:32:36,039 --> 00:32:37,199
That's true.

537
00:32:37,199 --> 00:32:41,159
How did you know the reply from the court

538
00:32:41,159 --> 00:32:43,400
that Magistrate Zheng received?

539
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,710
Because I wrote these replies.

540
00:32:50,270 --> 00:32:52,370
We come here for work.

