576
00:34:47,610 --> 00:34:50,220
I guess he won't hire me.

577
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:53,310
What are you talking about? I don't understand.

578
00:34:53,310 --> 00:34:55,020
Nothing.

579
00:34:55,020 --> 00:34:59,980
Brother, I missed you so much when I was outside.

580
00:34:59,980 --> 00:35:01,670
Silly girl.

581
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:03,960
