590
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:45,380
Does he still live here now?

591
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:49,750
You... Were you talking about a witch doctor?

592
00:35:49,750 --> 00:35:53,180
The man who used to tell you stories, living behind our house.

593
00:35:53,180 --> 00:35:55,480
